    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n      <strong>School:</strong>&nbsp;enchantment&nbsp;(compulsion)&nbsp;[mind-affecting];\n    <br>\n    <strong>Level:</strong>&nbsp;Cleric 2;\n    <strong>Domain:</strong>&nbsp;Good 2, Luck 2;\n    \n    \n    \n    <br>\n    <strong>Components:</strong>&nbsp;V, S, F, DF<br>\n    \n      <strong>Casting Time:</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Range:</strong>&nbsp;touch<br>\n    \n    <strong>Target:</strong>&nbsp;living creature touched<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;1 min./level<br>\n    \n        <strong>Saving Throw:</strong>&nbsp;None\n        <br>\n        <strong>Spell Resistance:</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  \n\n\n<p>\n<i>Aid </i>grants the target a +1 morale bonus on attack rolls and saves against fear effects, plus temporary hit points equal to 1d8 + caster level (to a maximum of 1d8+10 temporary hit points at caster level 10th).\n</p>\n<hr/>\n\n\n\n</div>\n",
